{"title":"Theme Showcase","date":"2021-02-20T16:17:44.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Feb 21, 2021","L":"02/21/2021","MM-DD":"02-21"},"link":"2021/02/21/Theme-Showcase","tags":["Hexo"],"updated":"2021-02-20T17:17:25.144Z","content":"<p><a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/post/inside-theme-showcase#fnref1\" target=\"_blank\">Inside Theme Showcase</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"different-heading-(h1)\"><strong>Different Heading (h1)</strong><a title=\"#different-heading-(h1)\" href=\"#different-heading-(h1)\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"h2\">h2<a title=\"#h2\" href=\"#h2\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"h3\">h3<a title=\"#h3\" href=\"#h3\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"h4\">h4<a title=\"#h4\" href=\"#h4\"></a></h4>\n<h5 id=\"h5\">h5<a title=\"#h5\" href=\"#h5\"></a></h5>\n<h6 id=\"h6\">h6<a title=\"#h6\" href=\"#h6\"></a></h6>\n<h1 id=\"image-(click-to-zoom-in/out)\"><strong>Image (click to zoom in/out)</strong><a title=\"#image-(click-to-zoom-in/out)\" href=\"#image-(click-to-zoom-in/out)\"></a></h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;!-- new line --&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">![space](address)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;!-- new line --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/006SqI8Pgy1gnui7hk2efj31xg10jqv5.jpg\" alt=\"space\" class=\"φbs\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"inline-image\"><strong>Inline Image</strong><a title=\"#inline-image\" href=\"#inline-image\"></a></h1>\n<p>?</p>\n<h1 id=\"with-link\"><strong>With Link</strong><a title=\"#with-link\" href=\"#with-link\"></a></h1>\n<p>?</p>\n<h1 id=\"hr\"><strong>hr</strong><a title=\"#hr\" href=\"#hr\"></a></h1>\n<p><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"list\"><strong>List</strong><a title=\"#list\" href=\"#list\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"unordered-list\">Unordered list<a title=\"#unordered-list\" href=\"#unordered-list\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>list item</li>\n<li>list item</li>\n<li>list item\n<ul>\n<li>list item</li>\n<li>list item\n<ul>\n<li>list item</li>\n<li>list item</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ordered-list\">Ordered list<a title=\"#ordered-list\" href=\"#ordered-list\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>list item</li>\n<li>list item\n<ol>\n<li>list item</li>\n<li>list item\n<ol>\n<li>list item</li>\n<li>list item</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"checklist\">Checklist<a title=\"#checklist\" href=\"#checklist\"></a></h2>\n<ul class=\"φbu\" class=\"φbu\">\n<li><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\"><i></i>Do homework</li>\n<li><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\"><i></i>Write code</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"table\"><strong>Table</strong><a title=\"#table\" href=\"#table\"></a></h1>\n<div class=\"φbt\"><div class=\"φbv\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">Left align</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:right\">Right align</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">Middle align</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">block</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right\">block</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">block</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">block</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right\">block</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">block</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h2 id=\"headless\">Headless<a title=\"#headless\" href=\"#headless\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"φbt\"><div class=\"φbv\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"padding:0\"></th>\n<th style=\"padding:0\"></th>\n<th style=\"padding:0\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">One</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Two</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Three</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h1 id=\"blockquote\"><strong>Blockquote</strong><a title=\"#blockquote\" href=\"#blockquote\"></a></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/tag-plugins.html\" target=\"_blank\">Hexo标签插件</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% blockquote [author[, source]] [link] [source_link_title] %&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">content</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;% endblockquote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote><p>Do not just seek happiness for yourself. Seek happiness for all. Through kindness. Through mercy.</p>\n<footer><strong>David Levithan</strong><cite>Wide Awake</cite></footer></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"code-block\"><strong>Code Block</strong><a title=\"#code-block\" href=\"#code-block\"></a></h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> message = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;Welcome to my blog!&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(message);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"code-block-with-caption\"><strong>Code Block with Caption</strong><a title=\"#code-block-with-caption\" href=\"#code-block-with-caption\"></a></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/tag-plugins.html\" target=\"_blank\">Hexo标签插件</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% codeblock [title] [lang:language] [url] [link text] [additional options] %&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">code snippet</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;% endcodeblock %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>You need to specify options in <code>[additional options]</code>, e.g.<code>line_number: false first_line:5</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/006SqI8Pgy1gnui6w0v98j30k7084t8q.jpg\" alt=\"Extra options\" class=\"φbs\"></p>\n<p>e.g. 附加说明和网址</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><figcaption><span>_.compact</span><a href=\"http://underscorejs.org/#compact\">Underscore.js</a></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">_.compact([0, 1, false, 2, &#39;&#39;, 3]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#x3D;&gt; [1, 2, 3]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"timeline\"><strong>Timeline</strong><a title=\"#timeline\" href=\"#timeline\"></a></h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">::: timeline</span><br><span class=\"line\">- xxx 2020&#x2F;04&#x2F;10</span><br><span class=\"line\">- xxx 2020&#x2F;04&#x2F;11</span><br><span class=\"line\">- xxx 2020&#x2F;04&#x2F;12</span><br><span class=\"line\">- xxx 2020&#x2F;04&#x2F;13</span><br><span class=\"line\">:::</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<div class=\"φbw\"><ul>\n<li>xxx 2020/04/10</li>\n<li>xxx 2020/04/11</li>\n<li>xxx 2020/04/12</li>\n<li>xxx 2020/04/13</li>\n</ul>\n</div><h1 id=\"collapsable\"><strong>Collapsable</strong><a title=\"#collapsable\" href=\"#collapsable\"></a></h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">::: collapse Click to show a secret</span><br><span class=\"line\">🥱 You got me !</span><br><span class=\"line\">:::</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<details><summary>Click to show a secret</summary><p>🥱 You got me !</p>\n</details><h1 id=\"footnote\"><strong>footnote</strong><a title=\"#footnote\" href=\"#footnote\"></a></h1>\n<p>?</p>\n","next":{"title":"Hello World","link":"2021/02/18/hello-world"},"plink":"http://example.com/2021/02/21/Theme-Showcase/","toc":[{"id":"different-heading-(h1)","title":"Different Heading (h1)","index":"1","children":[{"id":"h2","title":"h2","index":"1.1","children":[{"id":"h3","title":"h3","index":"1.1.1"}]}]},{"id":"image-(click-to-zoom-in/out)","title":"Image (click to zoom in&#x2F;out)","index":"2"},{"id":"inline-image","title":"Inline Image","index":"3"},{"id":"with-link","title":"With Link","index":"4"},{"id":"hr","title":"hr","index":"5"},{"id":"list","title":"List","index":"6","children":[{"id":"unordered-list","title":"Unordered list","index":"6.1"},{"id":"ordered-list","title":"Ordered list","index":"6.2"},{"id":"checklist","title":"Checklist","index":"6.3"}]},{"id":"table","title":"Table","index":"7","children":[{"id":"headless","title":"Headless","index":"7.1"}]},{"id":"blockquote","title":"Blockquote","index":"8"},{"id":"code-block","title":"Code Block","index":"9"},{"id":"code-block-with-caption","title":"Code Block with Caption","index":"10"},{"id":"timeline","title":"Timeline","index":"11"},{"id":"collapsable","title":"Collapsable","index":"12"},{"id":"footnote","title":"footnote","index":"13"}]}